<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
Dear <%= @user.name %>,
<p>
  A request to reset your password in the <%= APPLICATION_NAME %> website has been received.
</p>
<p>
  You can reset your password by going to <%= link_to @url, @url %> in the next <%= pluralize(@hours_to_reset_password,"hour") %>.
</p>
<p>
  If you didn't submit a request to reset your password, feel free to ignore this email.
</p>
</body>
</html>